Body Panel Precautions – Speedster/ VX 200

Do not sit, or lean heavily on the body panels.

The body panels must not be subjected to excessive deflecting; the gel coat can crack. These cracks can take up to 3 months to become visible.

The gel coat is a thin layer of resin that seals the outer surface of the body panels and forms a smooth base for the paint.
